metadata.name: STAIRS TO NEXT LEVEL OF CONSCIUSNESS
metadata.description: This digital painting is my representation of the world of an Architect, Artist, Spitirual human being . The style remember the Bauhaus movement but revisited in a new modern key. The stairs represent the way to reach an upper level of human evolution and so, a next level of consciusness. The woman is dancing and happily joining her life journey. The vertical stripes are the frame of a window we see through.
